ictional story.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story-focused exploration - Explore the dark places of the people that you thought they are good and reveal their dark secrets.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychological Horror</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tags:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Indie Horror Adventure Single Player</p></li></ul>",
